latestPosts.caption:
SAVE THIS recipe for the perfect summer mango and avocado salad ☀️🥭 🥑

I don’t have to worry about getting detailed recipes and instant solutions with @meta.ai 🩵

Salad & Dressing recipe - 
Salad Ingredients: 
- 2 Mangoes
- 1 Avacado 
- Onion 
- ⁠Cucumber
- Cherry tomatoes 
- Mint leaves / Cilantro 

Dressing Ingredients: 
- Olive oil 
- ⁠Lemon juice 
- ⁠Honey 
- ⁠Salt 
- ⁠Pepper 
- ⁠Tajin powder 

Add some pumpkin seeds for a little crunch. If you are not a fan of feta, you can swap it with nuts and seeds of your choice. Toss in some fresh salad leaves for that extra freshness, totally optional, but always adds a nice touch to the salad. 

Tip : Make sure to remember one avocado to two mangoes is the perfect ratio.
